{"tid":783480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【審查版引擎】Google逾千員工聯署 反對為入中國市場「跪低」","createTime":"2018-08-17T14:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T09:15:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12870d70c0e235eed621ea986eb7140c408ca82a","tid":783480,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"近日有傳媒報道Google為重返中國市場「跪低」，秘密建立符合中國審查要求的搜尋引擎，員工對此非常不滿，逾千名員工聯署反對Google為中國度身訂造審查版搜索引擎。<br />\n<br />\n員工在聯署信中要求高層提高政策透明度，稱員工所得的資訊不足，難以在工作上「做出道德上明智的決定」，又投訴公司涉嫌隱瞞有關項目，令員工竟要透過傳媒報道才得知此事。<br />\n稱他們目前在工作時沒有所需的訊息作出道德決定，並投訴大部份員工都只是透過傳媒報道才得知有關搜尋引擎項目。<br />\nGoogle員工已不是首次就公司的道德決策去信高層表達關注。今年4月，3,100名員工曾向集團行政總裁皮查遞交請願信，要求集團停止協助美國國防部做人工智能試驗「Project Maven」，因為當中涉及的影像辯識技術，或會應用在無人機空襲行動上。Google於6月份決定不與軍方續約。"},{"pid":"a6c7a9d3576d7f953e6526b38d83e965b045bdd8","tid":783480,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:37:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180817/58573425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58573425&d=a%2BaxZY3u0KrxO7NzBs9VX9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b5b2e7aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58573425&h=8c7af731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180817/58573425</a>"},{"pid":"82e867706e2ece1f00493232d78cbff880cb5fe1","tid":783480,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"反對支那版Gooogle就話姐，搞鳩國防部科研.....班憨鳩職員係咪淨係想用鍵盤打贏支國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b441ca6a21c3193024af15c4fb8b2889e2235173","tid":783480,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845d32f3cc7b5eaed24b0b0bc13cb6b66c270a7d","tid":783480,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"Don&rsquo;t be evil? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f713d8d839d013be601b60a85b3687e01bbd2374","tid":783480,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"鬼叫歐盟冇錢要罰Google幾百億美金咩"},{"pid":"7141805a40a2d9696c68714d564ae5d9a2c4fca9","tid":783480,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"又話中旨係要比人乜都可以容易search到<br />\n宜家整filter比支那用<br />\n唔比人屌就奇"},{"pid":"d5f0338f65d77eb9e54eb2449611a4c130e20e8b","tid":783480,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be92313af45eac43cf03a7e0c71c58f6f494ca54","tid":783480,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8eb72320c2a21b33331ba6a5b1f47423fc468bcf","tid":783480,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"最應該聯署個班係 QQ同百度既老闆 股東 同員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f9bb56265d99a9b1666ca9f85d46554a9f4a2e","tid":783480,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":